lead_paragraph: Bowling Green will be a four-touchdown underdog coming into Ohio Stadium on Saturday, but new Falcons coach Mike Jinks said he welcomes the chance to "shock the world."

headline.print_headline: MAC Power Bowling Green Will Try to 'Shock' Buckeyes
